---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "朝圣故事 | Kailash 2026";
const description = "来自世界各地朝圣者的真实故事。冈仁波齐转山之旅如何改变他们的人生，带来心灵的觉醒与转变。";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-kailash-dark py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">朝圣故事</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Pilgrim Stories</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">巡礼者の物語</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">순례자 이야기</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="zh">真实旅程 · 心灵转变 · 神圣回忆</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Real Journeys · Transformative Experiences · Sacred Memories</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">真実の旅 · 心の変容 · 神聖な思い出</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">진실한 여정 · 마음의 변화 · 신성한 추억</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stories Grid -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-kailash-light">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Story 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="zh">"当翻越卓玛拉垭口的那一刻，我终于明白什么是信仰的力量。5630米，这是我人生到达的最高点，也是心灵的最高点。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"The moment I crossed Drolma La pass, I finally understood the power of faith. At 5,630 meters, this is the highest point of my life, and also the highest point of my soul."</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"ドマラ峠を越えた瞬間、信仰の力とは何かを初めて理解しました。標高5630メートル、これは私の人生で最も高い地点であり、同時に心の最も高い地点でもあります。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"도마라 고개를 넘는 순간, 신앙의 힘이 무엇인지 처음으로 이해했습니다. 해발 5630미터, 이것은 제 인생에서 가장 높은 곳이자 동시에 마음의 가장 높은 곳입니다."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">张</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="zh">张先生</p>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Mr. Zhang</p>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">張さん</p>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">장 씨</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">北京 · 2025年9月</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="zh">"带着70岁的母亲完成转山，她在止热寺前双手合十的样子，是我这辈子见过最美的画面。朝圣无关年龄，只关乎心愿。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"I completed the kora with my 70-year-old mother. Watching her pray at Drirapuk Monastery was the most beautiful sight I've ever seen. Pilgrimage knows no age—it only requires a sincere heart."</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"70歳の母と共にコーラを完成させました。ディラプク寺で母が手を合わせる姿は、私が今まで見た中で最も美しい光景でした。巡礼は年齢に関係なく、心の願いに関わるものです。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"70세 어머니와 함께 코라를 완주했습니다. 디라푹 사원에서 어머니가 손을 모으는 모습은 제가 지금까지 본 것 중 가장 아름다운 광경이었습니다. 순례는 나이와 상관없이 마음의 소원과 관련된 것입니다."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">李</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="zh">李女士</p>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Ms. Li</p>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">李さん</p>
                <p class="font-medium" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">이 씨</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">成都 · 2025年6月</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic">"Kailash is the abode of Lord Shiva. I waited 3 years for the permit. The 52km kora changed my perspective on life forever."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">R</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Rajesh Kumar</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delhi, India · 2024</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 4 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="zh">"作为一名基督徒，我不确定会发生什么。但冈仁波齐超越了任何单一宗教。站在那座神圣的山峰前，我感受到了无法言喻的存在。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"As a Christian, I wasn't sure what to expect. But Kailash transcends any single religion. Standing before that sacred peak, I felt a presence that words cannot describe."</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"クリスチャンとして、何が待っているか分かりませんでした。しかしカイラスはあらゆる宗教を超越しています。あの神聖な峰の前に立つと、言葉では表現できない存在感を感じました。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"기독교인으로서 무엇이 기다리고 있을지 확신하지 못했습니다. 하지만 카일라스는 어떤 단일 종교도 뛰어넘습니다. 그 신성한 봉우리 앞에 서자, 말로 표현할 수 없는 존재감을 느꼈습니다."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">S</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Sarah Johnson</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">London, UK · 2024</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 5 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="zh">"这是我的第七次转山。每次我都能发现新的东西。山没有变，但我变了。每一圈都剥离了另一层自我，揭示出更真实的本我。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"This was my seventh kora. Each time I discover something new. The mountain doesn't change, but I do. Every circuit peels away another layer of ego, revealing a more authentic self."</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"これは7回目のコーラでした。毎回新しい発見があります。山は変わらないが、私は変わる。一周ごとに自我の層が剥がれ、より真実の自分が現れる。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"이것은 제 7번째 코라였습니다. 매번 새로운 것을 발견합니다. 산은 변하지 않지만, 저는 변합니다. 매 바퀴가 자아의 또 다른 층을 벗겨내어 더 진실한 자신을 드러냅니다."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">丁</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Tenzin Dorje</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Lhasa, Tibet · 2024</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 6 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="zh">"我为了冒险而来，却带着转变的心离开。韩国朝圣团成为了我的家人。我们一起受苦，一起欢笑，一起成长。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"I came for the adventure, I left with a transformed heart. The Korean pilgrimage group became my family. We suffered together, laughed together, and grew together."</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"冒険のために来て、変容した心を持って去りました。韓国の巡礼団が私の家族になりました。共に苦しみ、共に笑い、共に成長しました。"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"모험을 위해 왔지만, 변화된 마음을 가지고 떠났습니다. 한국 순례단이 제 가족이 되었습니다. 함께 고생하고, 함께 웃고, 함께 성장했습니다."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">朴</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Park Min-ji</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Seoul, Korea · 2023</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Legends -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="zh">神圣传说</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Sacred Legends</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">神聖な伝説</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">신성한 전설</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧘</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="zh">米拉日巴的胜利</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Milarepa's Victory</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ミラレパの勝利</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">밀라레파의 승리</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="zh">11世纪的藏传佛教瑜伽士米拉日巴在冈仁波齐附近的洞穴中修行。当苯教祭司挑战他比赛登上山顶时，米拉日巴在日出时飞到了山顶，证明了佛教修行的力量。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">The 11th-century Tibetan yogi Milarepa meditated in a cave near Kailash. When challenged by a Bon priest to race to the summit, Milarepa flew there at sunrise, proving the power of Buddhist practice.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">11世紀のチベットのヨギ・ミラレパはカイラス近くの洞窟で修行しました。ボン教の祭司が頂上への競争を挑んだ時、ミラレパは日の出と共に飛んで頂上に着き、仏教修行の力を証明しました。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">11세기 티베트 요기 밀라레파는 카일라스 근처 동굴에서 수행했습니다. 본교 사제가 정상까지의 경쟁을 제안했을 때, 밀라레파는 일출과 함께 날아가 정상에 도착하여 불교 수행의 힘을 증명했습니다.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🐴</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="zh">格萨尔王的马蹄印</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Gesar King's Horse Tracks</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ゲサル王の馬の蹄跡</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">게살 왕의 말발굽 자국</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="zh">传说中的藏族英雄格萨尔王在他的史诗征战中在冈仁波齐的悬崖上留下了马蹄印。这些印记至今可见，提醒朝圣者纯洁心灵的人会得到神圣保护。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">The legendary Tibetan hero Gesar King left hoof prints on Kailash's cliffs during his epic campaigns. These marks are still visible, reminding pilgrims that those with pure hearts receive divine protection.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">伝説のチベットの英雄ゲサル王は、彼の叙事詩的な戦役の途中でカイラスの崖に馬の蹄跡を残しました。これらの跡は今も見ることができ、純粋な心を持つ者が神聖な保護を受けることを巡礼者に思い出させます。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">전설의 티베트 영웅 게살 왕은 그의 서사적 전투 중 카일라스 절벽에 말발굽 자국을 남겼습니다. 이 흔적들은 아직도 보이며, 순수한 마음을 가진 사람들이 신성한 보호를 받는다는 것을 순례자들에게 상기시킵니다.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🙏</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="zh">108种慈悲</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">108 Forms of Compassion</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">108の慈悲</h3>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">108가지 자비</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="zh">在卓玛拉垭口，朝圣者留下衣物和个人物品作为供品。这象征着放下执着和负面业力。这个传统代表着菩萨修行的108种慈悲形式。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">At Drolma La pass, pilgrims leave clothing and personal items as offerings. This symbolizes leaving behind attachments and negative karma. The tradition represents the 108 forms of compassion practiced by bodhisattvas.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ドマラ峠で、巡礼者は衣服や個人物品を供え物として残します。これは執着と悪いカルマを置いていくことを象徴しています。この伝統は菩薩が修行する108の慈悲の形を表しています。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">도마라 고개에서 순례자들은 옷과 개인 물품을 제물로 남깁니다. 이것은 집착과 부정적인 업을 남겨두는 것을 상징합니다. 이 전통은 보살이 수행하는 108가지 자비의 형태를 나타냅니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-kailash-gold">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">您完成了转山吗？</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Have You Completed the Kora?</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">コーラを完走しましたか？</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">코라를 완주하셨나요?</h2>
        <p class="text-kailash-dark/80 mb-8" data-lang-content="zh">分享您的故事，激励未来的朝圣者。您的经历可能成为某人开始神圣之旅的鼓励。</p>
        <p class="text-kailash-dark/80 mb-8" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Share your story and inspire future pilgrims. Your experience could be the encouragement someone needs to begin their sacred journey.</p>
        <p class="text-kailash-dark/80 mb-8" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">あなたの物語を共有して、未来の巡礼者を励ましてください。あなたの経験が、誰かが神聖な旅を始めるために必要な励ましになるかもしれません。</p>
        <p class="text-kailash-dark/80 mb-8" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">당신의 이야기를 공유하고 미래의 순례자들에게 영감을 주세요. 당신의 경험이 누군가가 신성한 여정을 시작하는 데 필요한 격려가 될 수 있습니다.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-kailash-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-dark/90 transition" data-lang-content="zh">分享您的故事</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-kailash-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-dark/90 transition" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Share Your Story</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-kailash-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-dark/90 transition" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">あなたの物語を共有</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-kailash-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-dark/90 transition" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">당신의 이야기 공유</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>